organization.description:
Borinquen Medical Centers of Miami-Dade provide a comprehensive range of health and social services to our culturally diverse community in Miami-Dade County. 

Services include internal Medicine, HIV, Pediatrics, Adolescent, OB/GYN Including Delivery, Family Planning, Healthy Start, Nutritionist, Dental Health, Child Immunizations, Behavioral Health, Psychiatry, Substance Abuse, Case Management, Prevention Education, Podiatry, Optometry / Opticals, Speech Language and Communication Disorders Treatments, Laboratory, X-Ray, Pharmacy, Medicaid Eligibility.
organization.name: BORINQUEN MEDICAL CENTERS OF MIAMI-DADE
